casebody.data:
James Flint LEE, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 80779 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: August 28, 2018 Melissa A. Featherston, St. Louis, MO, for appellant. Robert J. Bartholomew, Jr., Jefferson City, MO, for respondent. Before Division One: Thomas H. Newton, Presiding Judge, Cynthia L. Martin, Judge and Gary D. Witt, Judge

ORDER

Per curiam:

James Lee ("Lee") appeals the denial of his motion for post-conviction relief under Rule 24.035 by the Circuit Court of Clay County, Missouri following an evidentiary hearing. We affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
